modName: An Honest Living - New Voice Acted Repeatable Jobs
summary: This is a mod that aims to add a large number of small repeatable jobs seamlessly to Skyrim. They are mostly distributed to already existing NPCs. You can talk to innkeepers to serve drinks, clean swords for a blacksmith, or be a sailor on a ship.
descriptionHtml: This is a mod that aims to add a large number of small repeatable jobs seamlessly to Skyrim. They are mostly distributed to already existing NPCs. You can talk to innkeepers to serve drinks, clean swords for a blacksmith, or be a sailor on a ship.
